---
// 静态产品展示组件 - SSG优化
---
<section class="w-full bg-white py-10 animate-fade-in">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-2">HOT RECOMMENDED PRODUCTS</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl">From the procurement of raw materials to assembly of products, we are strict in every process to strictly achieve the international quality management system and product quality.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center w-32 md:w-40">
        <img src="/skid1.webp" alt="滑移装载机" class="w-28 md:w-36 h-20 md:h-24 mb-2 object-cover rounded" loading="lazy">
        <span class="font-semibold text-center text-sm md:text-base">Wheeled Skid Steer Loader</span>
        <a href="/products/skid-steer-loader" class="mt-2 px-3 md:px-4 py-1 bg-[#e60012] text-white rounded text-xs font-bold">View Details</a>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center w-32 md:w-40">
        <img src="/backhoe.webp" alt="挖掘装载机" class="w-28 md:w-36 h-20 md:h-24 mb-2 object-cover rounded" loading="lazy">
        <span class="font-semibold text-center text-sm md:text-base">Backhoe Loader</span>
        <a href="/products/backhoe-loader" class="mt-2 px-3 md:px-4 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-white rounded text-xs font-bold">View Details</a>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center w-32 md:w-40">
        <img src="/telescopic.webp" alt="伸缩臂叉车" class="w-28 md:w-36 h-20 md:h-24 mb-2 object-cover rounded" loading="lazy">
        <span class="font-semibold text-center text-sm md:text-base">Telescopic Handler</span>
        <a href="/products/telescopic-handler" class="mt-2 px-3 md:px-4 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-white rounded text-xs font-bold">View Details</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- 轮播指示点 -->
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-2">
      <button class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#e60012]" aria-label="当前"></button>
      <button class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-gray-300" aria-label="切换"></button>
      <button class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-gray-300" aria-label="切换"></button>
      <button class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-gray-300" aria-label="切换"></button>
      <button class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-gray-300" aria-label="切换"></button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 